This suggests that cs.SI (Signal Processing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the use of CSs with quadrature amplitude modulation (QAM) alphabet, which is a common modulation scheme in communication systems.
